name: Resin Cuff Red
description:
The collection – Resin Heaven
 
Handmade and polished resin jewellery made in my studio. Colours are numerous and hand mixed colours can be made to compliment other items, such as clothing colours.
 
Wide bangle internal Diameter: oval shape 65 x 70mm, Max Height: 45mm. Finish – matt.
 
Note: all measurements are approximate due to handmade nature of bangle and may change when sanded

name: Resin Circles Brooch
description: Resin Brooch in burgendy, organge and purple - stunning colours. Each circular resin colour is approx 3cm wide. The resin colour is hand mixed and poured to create unique designs.

name: Kimono Stud Earrings Purple
description:
Vintage Kimono stud earrings. Vintage kimono fabric is captured in all its glory under resin glass. Earring is approximately 2cm wide.
 
Custom colours and sizes available.
 

I travelled to Japan for my honeymoon a few years ago
and I completely fell in love and lust with their beautiful silk kimonos. I
returned to Australia with one kimono for myself but I wanted more..........
hence my new vintage kimono jewellery collection.
 
I purchase silk vintage kimonos from Japan and give them
new life as jewellery – kimono kanzashi flower brooches and necklaces and kimono resin brooch.
Each piece of jewellery is unique and limited edition as the vintage kimono
fabric is bought one at a time and loving folded into new creations.

name: Kimono Clutch Bag
description:
Vintage Kimono clutch handbag. Vintage kimono fabric is captured in all its glory this stunning clutch. Clutch is approximately 13cm wide and 30cm long.
 
The wrist strap allows you to keep your hands free to enjoy a champagne and canape. Inside pockets is large enough to hold all you need for a great night out.
 
Custom colours and sizes available.
